---
import { CONFIG } from "../config";

---

<section id="demo" class="w-full py-16 px-4 md:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold mb-4 text-center">Галерия</h2>
    <p class="text-white/80 text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">Вижте RAYDAR в действие с тези впечатляващи визуализирани изображения</p>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="group">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <img 
            src="/demos/glass_menagerie.png" 
            alt="Колекция от стъклени сфери" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Стъклени сфери с отражение и пречупване</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <img 
            src="/demos/cornell.png" 
            alt="Cornell box сцена" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Интериорна сцена с глобално осветление</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <img 
            src="/demos/metallic_showroom.png" 
            alt="Метални материали" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Сцена с метални материали и сложни отражения</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <img 
            src="/demos/colorful_caustics.png" 
            alt="Демонстрация на каустика" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Демонстрация на каустика</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <img 
            src="/demos/nested_materials.png" 
            alt="Сцена с различни материали" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Вложени материали и сложно осветление</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="group">
        <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden cursor-pointer transform transition-transform hover:scale-105">
          <img 
            src="/demos/festive.png" 
            alt="Празнична сцена" 
            class="w-full h-64 object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-white/80 text-sm group-hover:text-white transition-colors">Празнична сцена с разнообразни светлинни ефекти</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="mt-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold mb-8 text-center">Представяне на проекта</h3>
      
  <div class="mt-16 w-full max-w-4xl mx-auto animate-slide-up" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden pb-[56.25%] rounded-xl shadow-2xl">
      <iframe 
        src={`https://www.youtube.com/embed/${CONFIG.youtubeVideo.id}`} 
        class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full"
        title="RAYDAR Demo Video"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" 
        allowfullscreen>
      </iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
          
      
      <p class="text-center text-white/80 mt-4">
        Кратко видео представяне на проекта и неговите възможности
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>